name: QuantLink
description:
Quantlink connects portfolio managers, quantitative researchers, and quant developers with hedge funds, proprietary trading firms and more.

We help quant trading firms identify and secure top candidates. With deep experience in quant trading recruitment, we have an excellent understanding of the requirements and challenges for successful PM and quant researcher hires in this fiercely competitive domain. Additionally, our experience of working with thousands of quants gives us a deep appreciation for what quants desire in their job search.

Limited opportunities, opaque hiring processes, and demanding interviews can be intimidating for job seekers. Quantlink is dedicated to assisting job seekers in overcoming these hurdles by utilising industry connections and knowledge to pinpoint the most promising positions and offer guidance.

For firms, challenges like talent scarcity, competition, and assessing technical skills can make locating and retaining quants difficult. Quantlink collaborates closely with PMs and quants to identify key attributes of successful quants. The company assists firms by utilising an extensive network to source suitable candidates, offering guidance on compensation and retention, and sharing insights on hiring trends and best practices to help beat the competition to hire.

Quantlink is committed to helping job seekers and firms navigate the intricate realm of quant recruiting and hiring, whether it is assisting a PM in transitioning from a discretionary bonus to a contractual payout or launching their own fund, guiding a researcher in becoming a sub-PM, helping a sub-PM achieve independence, or facilitating a quant's move from sell-side to buy-side.

Please follow the company to receive insights and learnings through Quantlink's blog posts.

Please message us if you are interested in learning more about the quant hiring market, as a candidate or client.

Coporate life no longer engaged me or inspired me, I wanted time freedom to do the things that mattered the most to me and be there for my daughters. However, I did not want to give up my 6-figure salary. 

I went looking to see what was around and found a little advertisement that seem to tick all my boxes, I knew this was the next step of my working life.

I now work with motivated professionals who are seeking their own career change to work a more flexible schedule and to further their own personal development and growth.

name: Bay State Veterinary Emergency & Specialty Services
description:
Bay State Veterinary Emergency & Specialty Services (BSVESS) is a state-of-the-art facility providing 24-hour emergency care and specialty services for companion animals. The hospital is staffed by experienced emergency clinicians and specialists in Internal Medicine, Surgery and Critical Care.

The hospital is located in Swansea, MA and is open 24-hours a day for emergency care. The hospital is staffed by internship-trained emergency clinicians who have constant access to specialists allowing them the ability to offer the best information and care available. Consultations with board-certified specialists in surgery and internal medicine are available by appointment.

The hospital is dedicated to providing the highest level of veterinary care to our patients in an atmosphere of compassion and excellence. Working in conjunction with Ocean State Veterinary Specialists to offer full spectrum of quality advanced care.

name: ICONS | America LLC
description:
ICONS|America is a leading manufacturer of injection molded tubes for the beauty, health, and wellness industry, focusing on cutting-edge In-Mold Label (“IML”) tube technology.

We collaborate with clients to create premium injection molded tubes boasting unmatched decorative options and luxurious finishes.

Located near Charlotte, North Carolina, ICONS|America offers a USA-based manufacturing solution, reducing carbon footprint and shortening the shipment delivery lead time.

ICONS| America is an ICONS Beauty Group company. Contact us via info@iconsbeauty.com For more information about ICONS, visit www.iconsbeautygroup.com
